程序包 com.taotaole.controller

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    CollectBookServlet
    Servlet implementation class CollectBookServlet 书的收藏列表的类
    方法有CollectBookServlet、doGet
    serialVersionUID初始为1L，长整型
    ContactOfSellerServlet
    Servlet implementation class ContactOfSellerServlet 类名ContactOfSellerServlet，是联系卖方的类 方法有ContactOfSellerServlet、doGet和doPost 返回值为空
    LaunchBookServlet
    Servlet implementation class LaunchBookServlet 类名LaunchBookServlet，是上传图书的类 类有的方法是LaunchBookServlet、doGet和doPost 长整型serialVersionUID，初始为1L
    LoginFilter
    类名 LoginFilter，登录类 方法有destroy、doFilter和init 实现借助了过滤器Filter
    LoginServlet
    Servlet implementation class LoginServlet
    RegisterServlet
    Servlet implementation class RegisterServlet
    RemoveCollectServlet
    Servlet implementation class RemoveCollectServlet 类名 RemoveCollectServlet
    RemoveTradeServlet
    Servlet implementation class RemoveTradeServlet 类名RemoveTradeServlet，移出交易类
    SerchCollectServlet
    Servlet implementation class SerchCollectServlet 类名 SerchCollectServlet，查询收藏类
    SerchServlet
    Servlet implementation class SerchServlet 绫诲SerchServlet锛绱㈢被
    SerchTradeServlet
    Servlet implementation class SerchTradeServlet 类名SerchTradeServlet，搜索交易类
    UpdateUserInfoServlet
    Servlet implementation class UpdateUserInfoServlet 类名UpdateUserInfoServlet，更新用户信息类
